</style>，但不是我们想要的对数依赖性；即使这个较弱的结果似乎也具有挑战性。</p><p>感谢所有花时间思考这个问题的人。</p><h3>这对 ARC 意味着什么</h3><p>在本节中，我将尝试简要描述这些问题和启发式估计器之间的关系。我将使用<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u0619QrWxQc"><u>本次演讲</u></a>中的上下文和符号。我不认为这次讨论足够详细，对那些还没有了解 ARC 工作背景的人来说有意义，而且我认为大多数读者应该等到我们明年发布更广泛的研究更新后再参​​与。</p><p> ARC 今年的主要活动之一是通过寻找算法、寻找硬度证据以及阐明我们所需的对齐应用实际需要哪些属性来完善启发式估计器的目标。这次比赛是这个过程的一部分。</p><p> 2023 年初，ARC 希望找到一个估计器<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="G"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，使得对于任何矩阵<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>和任何参数<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\pi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">π</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，启发式估计<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbb{G}\!\left( v^T A A^T v \mid \pi \right)"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="width: 6.637em;" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="margin-right: -0.167em; width: 0px; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mrow MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.593em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">v</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.12em;">T</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.12em;">T</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">v</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">∣</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">π</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.593em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>将是<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="v"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">v</span></span></span></span></span></span>的非负二次函数。我们提出的两个问题与在特殊情况下实现这一目标密切相关，其中<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span